{"tid":986042,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"點解啲親戚黎香港咁撚中意住人屋企？？？","createTime":"2019-01-18T06:40:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-18T14:35:56.000Z","uid":58335,"like":66,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"528e1bc9b8d7e435fa734d902098712f51ef0868","tid":986042,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T06:40:18.000Z","msg":"有個英國親戚遲啲返嚟<br />\n一家大細成三個人<br />\n又話探親又話剩<br />\n已經開到聲講屋企冇咩位你哋嚟住會好迫<br />\n<br />\n即係叫佢哋住酒店<br />\n佢地又嫌貴<br />\n屌你啦，黎旅行嫌貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n發覺老一輩嗰啲真係好鍾意住人屋企<br />\n你話屋企大都冇乜所謂<br />\n屌你香港啲屋咁撚細<br />\n佢哋又好意思打攪你先好嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2765c78743105d1b6adc5070af119791ff7a5d00","tid":986042,"uid":17889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T06:42:36.000Z","msg":"香港地方細真係好難招呼人過夜<br />\n有幾多人屋企有吉房"},{"pid":"6fcb16d7fd44e4df8607474ddcd4430cdd8ce896","tid":986042,"uid":58335,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"quote":{"pid":"2765c78743105d1b6adc5070af119791ff7a5d00","tid":986042,"uid":17889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T06:42:36.000Z","msg":"香港地方細真係好難招呼人過夜<br />\n有幾多人屋企有吉房"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T06:49:43.000Z","msg":"最仆街係要我瞓廳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3fd869a95c274f7c14dfe25b0037506ad387bcb","tid":986042,"uid":31962,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T06:51:37.000Z","msg":"酒店錢唔駛俾食左佢好過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申成日有親戚黎屈蛇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"082a052abed764b34474110b14569d2c5fa717d7","tid":9860